her personality along with her memories!

42
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:34,714
-Let's get out of here, Fujimii.
-What?

43
00:03:35,632 --> 00:03:38,801
-Sawa!
-This is one shady cult!

44
00:03:38,885 --> 00:03:40,553
Hold on!

45
00:03:43,473 --> 00:03:45,141
Oh, Uncle!

46
00:04:02,700 --> 00:04:05,495
I'm sorry to be harsh to a follower,

47
