52
00:04:22,679 --> 00:04:26,516
<i>He talks just like Aunt Misako,</i>
<i>who was into MLMs.</i>

53
00:04:27,809 --> 00:04:30,228
-A YouTuber?
-I can't find your videos!

54
00:04:30,311 --> 00:04:33,856
-I thought he was a cult leader.
-Where did you get that idea?

55
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:37,360
Takafumi's uncle is odd, but he's nice.

56
00:04:37,443 --> 00:04:39,696
But why are you with them, Fujimii?

57
00:04:40,196 --> 00:04:41,406
Well, you know…

58
00:04:41,489 --> 00:04:42,824
"Expi-uncle-docious"!

59
00:04:42,907 --> 00:04:44,325
"Unclebunga"!

60
00:04:44,409 --> 00:04:47,537
